{"tid":1833914,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人陪我食元氣…？","createTime":"2020-01-22T06:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T09:52:25.000Z","uid":277054,"like":102,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"c5e6a5c30d8f0086e9c72655d69b5f044ba8d268","tid":1833914,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:45:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">【5 / 2 感謝日聚餐】</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>活動</strong>：和你坐 &middot; 晚市三小時<br />\n<strong>時間</strong>：18:00-21:00（坐到截單更佳）<br />\n<strong>地點</strong>：代定（九龍區一/兩間分店）<br />\n<strong>衣着</strong>：出街look，口罩為記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dr04P8v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdr04P8v.jpg&h=d03f0f2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我真係好想食壽司呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&hellip;&hellip; </span><br />\n<br />\n機會嚟喇～ 嚟緊 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2 月 5 日 (星期三)</span></span> 就係一月一次嘅感謝日，我就梗係唔會放過呢個大好機會啦！一於同我哋去元氣到分享呢一份喜悅啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n讀緊書嘅朋友可以去溫書做功課，唔使溫書嘅鍾意打機煲劇玩啤牌又得啫！<br />\n<br />\n記得當日只可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">有限度消費 ($0~$10)</span></span>，從而<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">減低佢哋嘅營業額</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺用膳過程中唔刻意刁難職員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 須知道我哋針對嘅從來都係美心，而唔係佢嘅員工~ <br />\n<br />\n唔好戴文具玩具，我哋係嚟食飯，唔係做其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蟲蟲就自便啦，可能你想補充蛋白質呢~ <br />\n<br />\n至於食邊間，快啲講低你嘅意見啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/maysome_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaysome_bot&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=339f55cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/maysome_bot</a><br />\n<br />\n詳情請留意美心非官方後援會<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/maysome\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaysome&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=6a9b1beb\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/maysome</a>"},{"pid":"94e7fc693889c784d91b0439337f5c27e9ef0465","tid":1833914,"uid":13361,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:48:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />薑茶放題"},{"pid":"9921f58a74410bb5ab1d9d2df93eb9608d231587","tid":1833914,"uid":116917,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:52:21.000Z","msg":"睇標題就諗住入黎屌柒你<br />\n一入到黎把火就熄左<br />\n支持元氣，支持元氣收皮"},{"pid":"7afb0eb12ed2cb96f5b756ce716dab464802cd8d","tid":1833914,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3b8e3a1ca954e44db722353dc4de1c590315fb","tid":1833914,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9921f58a74410bb5ab1d9d2df93eb9608d231587","tid":1833914,"uid":116917,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:52:21.000Z","msg":"睇標題就諗住入黎屌柒你<br />\n一入到黎把火就熄左<br />\n支持元氣，支持元氣收皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:54:03.000Z","msg":"幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc2c784a5ff72113cbf19c2571ec1a35fc2d07d","tid":1833914,"uid":270307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:56:03.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c22d3a266725c59f14bc1a49c0653d2ec025d6","tid":1833914,"uid":148203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,